s/rashishrivastava/2026/04/15/mercors-23-year-old-billionaire-founders-grapple-with-employee-fraud-and-north-korean-infiltration/[Mercor’s 23-Year-Old Billionaire Founders Grapple With Employee Fraud And North Korean Infiltration](https://www.forbes.com/sites/rashishrivastava/2026/04/15/mercors-23-year-old-billionaire-founders-grapple-with-employee-fraud-and-north-korean-infiltration/)By[Rashi Shrivastava](https://www.forbes.com/sites/rashishrivastava/),\\nForbes Staff\\n\\nand[Anna Tong](https://www.forbes.com/sites/annatong/),\\nForbes Staff\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/annatong/2026/03/05/cursor-goes-to-war-for-ai-coding-dominance/[Cursor Goes To War For AI Coding Dominance](https://www.forbes.com/sites/annatong/2026/03/05/cursor-goes-to-war-for-ai-coding-dominance/)By[Rashi Shrivastava](https://www.forbes.com/sites/rashishrivastava/),\\nForbes Staff\\n\\nand[Rashi Shrivastava](https://www.forbes.com/sites/rashishrivastava/),\\nForbes Staff\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/amyfeldman/2025/08/11/longer-leash-on-life-inside-the-dog-longevity-startup-loyal/[Longer Leash On Life: Inside The Dog Longevity Startup](https://www.forbes.com/sites/amyfeldman/2025/08/11/longer-leash-on-life-inside-the-dog-longevity-startup-loyal/)By[Amy Feldman](https://www.forbes.com/sites/amyfeldman/),\\nSenior Editor\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/emilybaker-white/2025/08/18/with-trumps-tiktok-ban-on-hold-bytedance-is-quietly-launching-ai-apps/[With Trump’s TikTok Ban On Hold, ByteDance Is Quietly Launching AI Apps](https://www.forbes.com/sites/emilybaker-white/2025/08/18/with-trumps-tiktok-ban-on-hold-bytedance-is-quietly-launching-ai-apps/)By[Emily Baker-White](https://www.forbes.com/sites/emilybaker-white-1/),\\nSenior Writer\\n\\n[Can you solve today's phrase?](https://www.forbes.com/games/frase)\\n\\n## More From Innovation\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/davidphelan/2026/07/12/apple-ios-27-release-date-when-you-can-install-iphones-new-software---public-beta-near/\\n2 hours ago\\n\\n### [iOS 27 Release Date: Latest Schedule Confirms iPhone’s July Public Beta](https://www.forbes.com/sites/davidphelan/2026/07/12/apple-ios-27-release-date-when-you-can-install-iphones-new-software---public-beta-near/)\\nApple’s new iPhone software will go on general release in the fall, but signs suggest the public beta is almost upon us.\\nBy[David Phelan](https://www.forbes.com/sites/davidphelan/),\\nSenior Contributor\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/tomcoughlin/2026/07/12/memory-capacity-production-slowly-expanding-to-meet-ai-industry-demand/\\n3 hours ago\\n\\n### [Memory Capacity Production Slowly Expanding To Meet AI Industry Demand](https://www.forbes.com/sites/tomcoughlin/2026/07/12/memory-capacity-production-slowly-expanding-to-meet-ai-industry-demand/)\\nSamsung, SK hynix, Sandisk, Kioxia and Micron report building out new DRAM and NAND flash manufacturing and packaging facilities coming on line in late 2027 or 2028.\\nBy[Thomas Coughlin](https://www.forbes.com/sites/tomcoughlin/),\\nContributor\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/krisholt/2026/07/12/nyt-connections-answers-explained-monday-july-13/\\n5 hours ago\\n\\n### [NYT Connections Answers Explained: Monday, July 13](https://www.forbes.com/sites/krisholt/2026/07/12/nyt-connections-answers-explained-monday-july-13/)\\nNot sure what today's NYT Connections answers are all about? Find out just what the different words in today's grid mean and how they fit together.\\nBy[Kris Holt](https://www.forbes.com/sites/krisholt/),\\nContributor\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/joshuacohen/2026/07/12/lindsey-grahams-sudden-death-sparks-questions-about-cardiac-arrest/\\nTRENDING5 hours ago\\n\\n### [Lindsey Graham’s Sudden Death Sparks Questions About Cardiac Arrest](https://www.forbes.com/sites/joshuacohen/2026/07/12/lindsey-grahams-sudden-death-sparks-questions-about-cardiac-arrest/)\\nGraham's death sparks questions on cardiac arrest that is caused by an electrical malfunction in the heart that disrupts its pumping action. The heart then stops beating.\\nBy[Joshua P. Cohen](https://www.forbes.com/sites/joshuacohen/),\\nSenior Contributor\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/krisholt/2026/07/12/connections-hint-today-monday-july-13-answers-clues/\\n6 hours ago\\n\\n### [NYT Connections Hints And Answers: Monday, July 13](https://www.forbes.com/sites/krisholt/2026/07/12/connections-hint-today-monday-july-13-answers-clues/)\\nLooking for today's NYT Connections hints? Some help and the answers for today's game are right here to help keep your streak alive.\\nBy[Kris Holt](https://www.forbes.com/sites/krisholt/),\\nContributor\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/paultassi/2026/07/12/the-first-official-avengers-doomsday-cast-photo-is-a-nightmare/\\n6 hours ago\\n\\n### [The First Official ‘Avengers: Doomsday’ Cast Photo Is A Nightmare](https://www.forbes.com/sites/paultassi/2026/07/12/the-first-official-avengers-doomsday-cast-photo-is-a-nightmare/)\\nDisney has released the first full cast illustration of Avengers: Doomsday, and it reminds us just how bad this line-up is.\\nBy[Paul Ta\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c9b91bb5fb521caa\\\">>>\",\n  \"warning\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"865b1ac38bf42ef8\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Fetch\\n---\\nResponse body truncated after 750000 bytes.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"865b1ac38bf42ef8\\\">>>\"\n}"}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8193,"originalDetailKeys":["url","finalUrl","status","contentType","title","extractMode","extractor","externalContent","truncated","length","rawLength","wrappedLength","fetchedAt","tookMs","text","warning"],"status":200,"truncated":true},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783901675550}}
